 hidden magnetism, quantum\ncriticality and unconventional superconductivity in cuprate and heavy-electron\nsystems, such as CeRhIn5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2006 22:58:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2006 04:23:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
