values of $f$ and\n$\\omega$, signal-to-noise ratio is found to be maximum for square wave while it\nis minimum for modulus of sine and rectified sinusoidal waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Mar 2006 14:11:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
